animeTitle: Made in Abyss: Retsujitsu no Ougonkyou
animeDescription: Directly after the events of Made in Abyss Movie 3: Dawn of the Deep Soul, the third installment of Made in Abyss covers the adventure of Reg, Riko, and Nanachi in the Sixth Layer, The Capital of the Unreturned.
